				INSTALLATION GUIDE

You need the folowing to get things working :

PERL this product have been testet with Perl 5.005_02.

It is also recomendend that you install the folowing :

MySQL (or your favorite SQL server package).
Apache with PHP3

For the player.sh you need :

mpg123 (or something like it)
cat
head
tail
random

Copy the addtoplaylist.cgi to your cgi-bin directory and chmod/chown in the
way you want it!

The user that shall run player.sh must have write permissions to /tmp/playlist

Note that you should create an /tmp/allmp3files which includes all your online
MP3s if you want the player.sh to work correct.

//Daniel Andersson <daniel@sto.sema.se>
